1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,400
[Phranluang School]

2
00:00:09,480 --> 00:00:11,720
Though he was whipped
until he nearly breathed his last,

3
00:00:12,320 --> 00:00:15,280
with fine medicine and good nursing,

4
00:00:15,440 --> 00:00:16,680
Saen lived to see the day

5
00:00:16,720 --> 00:00:20,240
when his destiny soared far beyond anything
he had dared to dream.

6
00:00:21,440 --> 00:00:22,720
Here you are, Saen.

7
00:00:23,680 --> 00:00:25,920
Today you become a student of Phranluang.
Is that right?

8
00:00:26,600 --> 00:00:27,600
Yes, Chim.

9
00:00:28,440 --> 00:00:30,000
These are royal gifts for you.

10
00:00:30,680 --> 00:00:33,000
An iron chest for your belongings
and books,

11
00:00:33,280 --> 00:00:34,760
plain cloth, a sarong,

12
00:00:35,040 --> 00:00:37,000
and two round-necked shirts.

13
00:00:38,760 --> 00:00:41,200
You shall also have a room of your own.

14
00:00:43,280 --> 00:00:45,560
You shall have pillows,
a mosquito net, and a blanket.

15
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:47,760
You shall also be given three meals a day.

16
00:00:49,560 --> 00:00:51,280
But this may not excite you much,

17
00:00:51,960 --> 00:00:53,520
for you have seen such things
in your master's house.

18
00:00:55,560 --> 00:00:56,840
I am, of course, excited.

19
00:00:58,480 --> 00:01:00,480
I never thought I would
possess such things in my life.

20
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:03,040
Just to be able to dance
is more than enough.

21
00:01:04,360 --> 00:01:05,920
To think I shall wear a Khon mask...

22
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:09,040
You are indeed a fortunate soul.

23
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:18,480
Yet you seem unusually excited.

24
00:01:19,880 --> 00:01:21,320
Do you not already know?

25
00:01:22,360 --> 00:01:24,680
Master Rit received the same things
when he first came here.

26
00:01:25,720 --> 00:01:26,640
I do.

27
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:28,240
Yet it feels different.

28
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:32,120
I was only a servant then.

29
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:35,520
Now I am a student of the royal Khon.

30
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:38,320
I shall train, dance,

31
00:01:40,960 --> 00:01:42,240
and stay in the same place as Master Rit.

32
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:48,920
Oh. Go on now.

33
00:01:49,520 --> 00:01:51,400
The Royal Master may think
you are late for your first day.

34
00:01:52,720 --> 00:01:53,440
Indeed.

35
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:18,760
[Tanakorn Chuen-arom as Saen/Sand]

36
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:23,520
[Wacharathon Wongyai as Rak/Lucky]

37
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:27,640
[Worachai Areewong as Tan/Thank]

38
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:32,720
[Khitaphat Choothai as Chim/Charm]

39
00:02:32,920 --> 00:02:36,320
[Kornkamon Supaseripap as Vila/ViVi]

40
00:02:36,600 --> 00:02:40,560
[Rungtiva Sangngoen as Prink
Napat Seela as Rit/Ton]

41
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:44,160
[Chalisa Schaub as Kamala
Weeraachai Hatgovit as Phraya Banleng]

42
00:02:44,320 --> 00:02:48,520
[Nithiroj Simakamtorn as Phraya Dechanarong
Rattanachai Phakdirat as Khon Master]

43
00:02:58,680 --> 00:03:00,680
[Phranluang School]

44
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:14,000
Suanmisakawan is the training ground
of the royal Khon dancers.

45
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:17,000
Each morning and evening,
the sound of drums, ching,

46
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:18,880
and dancers shall be heard.

47
00:03:19,080 --> 00:03:21,000
Yet that afternoon was different.

48
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:24,880
For Rama, Thotsakan,
and Sida were all present.

49
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:28,720
Your rhythms are most harmonious.

50
00:03:31,160 --> 00:03:33,080
As though you were one,

51
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:34,920
Rak and Saen.

52
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:44,520
That is Tan.

53
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:47,840
A commoner's son,
taken under the wing of Phraya Dechanarong

54
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,720
and trained in Khon since childhood.

55
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:51,720
He used to dance the male role,

56
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:55,160
but when Master Rak arrived,
he was made to take the lady's role.

57
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:02,840
They say he looks sweet as sugar,

58
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:06,160
yet everyone knows he is bitter within.

59
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:11,360
Thotsakan,

60
00:04:11,600 --> 00:04:13,280
approach Sida.

61
00:04:28,640 --> 00:04:30,560
What is the matter with you, Saen?

62
00:04:31,320 --> 00:04:33,240
Do you not know how to dance?

63
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:34,440
Forgive me, sir.

64
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:36,840
Are you hurt, Tan?

65
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,240
It is nothing.

66
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:42,440
I stepped too hastily,

67
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:43,960
so I tripped.

68
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:45,760
The fault was mine.

69
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:46,840
Not yours.

70
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:54,040
Will you two dally any longer?

71
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:57,320
Well then, resume your positions.

72
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,840
See that you dance well this time.

73
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:03,080
Saen is pure of heart,

74
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:05,000
but Tan is a cunning man.

75
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:08,520
I know not why, yet when I see those eyes,

76
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:11,120
I feel he is not one to yield easily.

77
00:05:13,440 --> 00:05:14,200
Now then.

78
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:18,080
Rama, approach Sida.

79
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:47,960
Sida, are you fond of Thotsakan
and averse to Rama?!

80
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:49,880
Are you?

81
00:05:50,640 --> 00:05:51,680
Do better this time.

82
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:58,840
I feel uneasy at the sight of this.

83
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:01,880
Rak plays Rama,

84
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:05,160
yet Tan's heart
seethes like that of Thotsakan.

85
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:12,760
Despised Rama.

86
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:14,520
The loyal giant.

87
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:16,240
Vengeful Sida.

88
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:17,880
I could see it plainly.

89
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:21,200
From that afternoon on,
the matter would not end easily.

90
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:31,160
Why did you do such a thing?

91
00:06:32,280 --> 00:06:33,280
What are you speaking of?

92
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:39,800
You treated Master Rak ill.

93
00:06:41,080 --> 00:06:42,920
He has never hurt a soul.

94
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,360
Never?

95
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:48,520
What about me?

96
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:51,880
I have danced the male role since my youth.

97
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,120
Suddenly,

98
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:56,320
I was told to take the lady's role.

99
00:06:57,320 --> 00:07:00,120
Simply because he is a nobleman's son,
he is given the role of Rama.

100
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:02,120
Tan.

101
00:07:07,760 --> 00:07:09,400
Now I am Sida,

102
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:13,040
meekly waiting for Rama to woo me,

103
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:17,880
though once I stood tall as Rama.

104
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:23,560
It is strange indeed.

105
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:29,160
Saen was once but a servant,

106
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:32,280
yet he dances so well that I respect him.

107
00:07:33,960 --> 00:07:35,400
I am like him.

108
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:38,520
We are of the same kind.

109
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,920
Will you love him, Tan?

110
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,200
I know not.

111
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:47,080
I know only that

112
00:07:48,520 --> 00:07:50,120
he understands me better than anyone.

113
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:15,480
Your arrow flies true,

114
00:08:16,440 --> 00:08:18,160
yet your heart is astray.

115
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,520
Then let it be astray.

116
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:29,640
At least I can still dance as I please.

117
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:38,920
Saen,

118
00:08:39,500 --> 00:08:40,660
wait for me.

119
00:08:40,700 --> 00:08:41,700
Hurry, Tan,

120
00:08:41,740 --> 00:08:43,020
before the Royal Master returns and sees us.

121
00:08:43,340 --> 00:08:44,740
He may think us idle.

122
00:08:45,340 --> 00:08:47,460
The headmaster
asked me to measure the cloth,

123
00:08:47,560 --> 00:08:49,740
so I need someone of my size.

124
00:08:50,020 --> 00:08:52,100
That would be you, Saen.

125
00:08:53,380 --> 00:08:54,540
Hurry, then.

126
00:09:02,060 --> 00:09:03,260
You are too near, Tan.

127
00:09:07,500 --> 00:09:09,780
I was only measuring your chest.

128
00:09:09,900 --> 00:09:11,420
I did nothing at all.

129
00:09:12,580 --> 00:09:13,580
We must be off.

130
00:09:13,740 --> 00:09:14,760
I have other business to attend to.

131
00:09:40,460 --> 00:09:41,340
Master Rak,

132
00:09:41,620 --> 00:09:42,780
you returned early this afternoon.

133
00:09:42,820 --> 00:09:43,820
I was concerned.

134
00:09:46,020 --> 00:09:47,020
I returned to take some rest.

135
00:09:51,660 --> 00:09:52,780
What is the matter?

136
00:09:53,560 --> 00:09:55,020
Did your father scold you?

137
00:09:58,180 --> 00:09:59,180
It is nothing.

138
00:10:00,980 --> 00:10:03,060
But you do not seem as you usually do.

139
00:10:07,740 --> 00:10:09,520
Why do you concern yourself with my affairs?

140
00:10:14,220 --> 00:10:16,260
Because you are important to me.

141
00:10:26,140 --> 00:10:28,220
You have more important matters to attend to
than to trouble yourself with me.

142
00:10:31,300 --> 00:10:32,860
If I have offended you,

143
00:10:33,340 --> 00:10:34,660
please tell me,

144
00:10:35,140 --> 00:10:36,380
and I shall set it right.

145
00:10:38,820 --> 00:10:40,620
You have displeased me today.

146
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:44,300
What have I done?

147
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,260
I was there

148
00:10:47,920 --> 00:10:49,180
in the dressing room.

149
00:10:50,560 --> 00:10:51,820
I saw everything.

150
00:10:54,540 --> 00:10:55,860
I shall tell Tan

151
00:10:56,100 --> 00:10:57,420
not to trouble you again.

152
00:11:00,300 --> 00:11:02,090
That is not so.

153
00:11:04,900 --> 00:11:06,340
He kept pestering you.

154
00:11:15,900 --> 00:11:18,140
I do not think of him in that way.

155
00:11:19,140 --> 00:11:20,260
I am here to train

156
00:11:21,820 --> 00:11:23,260
and to attend to you.

157
00:11:28,340 --> 00:11:29,340
Very well.

158
00:11:31,880 --> 00:11:33,100
I give you my word.

159
00:11:36,160 --> 00:11:38,020
Since you have made yourself clear,

160
00:11:39,860 --> 00:11:42,300
let us say this never happened.

161
00:11:43,900 --> 00:11:44,780
As you wish.

162
00:12:16,460 --> 00:12:17,630
Saen,

163
00:12:18,580 --> 00:12:19,860
have some water.

164
00:12:23,100 --> 00:12:25,580
There is no need. I am not thirsty.

165
00:12:50,420 --> 00:12:51,500
Master Rak,

166
00:12:52,140 --> 00:12:53,640
I have brought you some water

167
00:12:54,380 --> 00:12:56,700
in gratitude for your kindness.

168
00:13:05,700 --> 00:13:06,620
Tan!

169
00:13:06,820 --> 00:13:08,460
Did you not already bring me this water?

170
00:13:08,940 --> 00:13:10,460
How dare you bring it to Master Rak?

171
00:13:12,180 --> 00:13:14,140
Because you would not accept it,

172
00:13:15,700 --> 00:13:17,980
I brought it to the one who deserved it.

173
00:13:22,140 --> 00:13:23,020
That is enough.

174
00:13:25,980 --> 00:13:26,980
Saen,

175
00:13:29,060 --> 00:13:30,340
go to the kitchen

176
00:13:31,820 --> 00:13:33,380
and see if there are any coconut pancakes.

177
00:13:34,180 --> 00:13:35,180
I should like some.

178
00:13:37,540 --> 00:13:38,340
As you wish.

179
00:13:49,180 --> 00:13:50,540
Your water, Master Rak.

180
00:14:15,940 --> 00:14:17,980
You have something to say, do you not?

181
00:14:23,260 --> 00:14:24,780
I am only curious

182
00:14:25,860 --> 00:14:28,220
whether Thotsakan desires Rama...

183
00:14:29,460 --> 00:14:31,900
or Sida as his spouse.

184
00:14:33,260 --> 00:14:34,620
What are you speaking of?

185
00:14:37,700 --> 00:14:39,180
Well...

186
00:14:40,140 --> 00:14:43,460
Thotsakan desires Sida,

187
00:14:43,660 --> 00:14:47,420
for she holds far greater sway over his heart
than Rama does.

188
00:14:49,620 --> 00:14:50,940
It seems...

189
00:14:51,940 --> 00:14:54,900
Thotsakan and Rama shall never lie together.

190
00:15:00,260 --> 00:15:01,820
I beg your pardon, Master Rak.

191
00:15:03,700 --> 00:15:06,020
This water is for servants.

192
00:15:06,740 --> 00:15:09,060
A master such as yourself
ought not to drink it.

193
00:15:13,500 --> 00:15:14,940
A master and his servant

194
00:15:15,900 --> 00:15:17,620
are not meant to be together.

195
00:15:48,780 --> 00:15:50,060
What has happened, Master?

196
00:15:56,140 --> 00:15:57,300
It is nothing.

197
00:16:01,900 --> 00:16:03,020
I am only hungry.

198
00:16:29,850 --> 00:16:31,150
Are you unwell, Master Rak?

199
00:16:39,970 --> 00:16:40,890
No.

200
00:16:43,730 --> 00:16:46,530
But you do not look well.

201
00:16:51,610 --> 00:16:54,490
Perhaps I am... nervous.

202
00:17:02,730 --> 00:17:05,170
You seem most prepared, Master Rak.

203
00:17:05,770 --> 00:17:08,730
It seems you are quite eager
to perform with me.

204
00:17:12,610 --> 00:17:13,810
Mind your tongue, Tan.

205
00:17:14,450 --> 00:17:15,570
It is almost time.

206
00:17:15,730 --> 00:17:16,930
You should go and make ready.

207
00:17:17,700 --> 00:17:18,970
Are you worried about me?

208
00:17:28,490 --> 00:17:29,550
That will do,

209
00:17:30,550 --> 00:17:31,490
Saen.

210
00:17:33,130 --> 00:17:34,850
He may stay or go as he will.

211
00:17:36,530 --> 00:17:37,690
We have guests.

212
00:17:38,530 --> 00:17:39,570
Do not start trouble.

213
00:17:39,610 --> 00:17:40,530
But Tan...

214
00:17:40,570 --> 00:17:41,890
I said that is enough.

215
00:17:44,690 --> 00:17:46,370
If he will not listen, so be it.

216
00:17:48,250 --> 00:17:49,530
But you must listen to me.

217
00:17:51,730 --> 00:17:54,330
How very loyal of you, Saen.

218
00:17:55,410 --> 00:17:57,460
You truly are to be envied, Master Rak.

219
00:17:59,930 --> 00:18:01,130
And you...

220
00:18:01,850 --> 00:18:03,130
Go where you will.

221
00:18:03,990 --> 00:18:05,690
Do not show your face here again.

222
00:18:07,950 --> 00:18:09,130
You smell foul.

223
00:18:33,810 --> 00:18:35,050
Are you angry with him?

224
00:18:37,130 --> 00:18:38,450
Is that why you said such things?

225
00:18:44,710 --> 00:18:46,010
His vile nature disgusts me,

226
00:18:47,690 --> 00:18:48,850
not his birth.

227
00:18:55,050 --> 00:18:56,490
I shall wait here.

228
00:18:59,610 --> 00:19:00,890
Should you require anything,

229
00:19:02,730 --> 00:19:03,930
please look to me.

230
00:19:07,570 --> 00:19:08,690
My thanks.

231
00:19:10,530 --> 00:19:11,690
But you need not worry.

232
00:19:13,850 --> 00:19:15,410
A show is a show.

233
00:19:17,530 --> 00:19:19,410
It has nothing to do with private matters.

234
00:19:29,570 --> 00:19:32,170
[Phranluang School]

235
00:20:37,490 --> 00:20:38,850
My apologies, Master Rak,

236
00:20:39,090 --> 00:20:40,170
for hurting you.

237
00:21:11,050 --> 00:21:12,380
Are you changing, Master Rak?

238
00:21:14,170 --> 00:21:15,010
Yes.

239
00:21:15,770 --> 00:21:17,170
This costume is too heavy.

240
00:21:18,170 --> 00:21:19,330
Allow me to help you.

241
00:21:47,330 --> 00:21:48,530
Are you weary?

242
00:21:51,770 --> 00:21:52,770
I am a little sore.

243
00:21:54,570 --> 00:21:55,810
Many thanks.

244
00:22:05,410 --> 00:22:06,770
Allow me to tend to your wound.

245
00:22:39,850 --> 00:22:41,010
Does it hurt?

246
00:22:57,050 --> 00:22:58,170
This way, please.

247
00:22:59,330 --> 00:23:00,230
Lead the way.
